ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 236, Manitoba
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 236 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA, with respect to the severe rainstorm that occurred from June 28, 2020 to July 5, 2020.
